          <p>LiNGUiD offers an auto-renewable subscription called "LiNGUiD Pro." Current subscription duration and price are displayed in the app before purchase. Subscriptions automatically renew unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Payment will be charged to your iTunes account. For more details on subscriptions, billing, and cancellation, please refer to our Privacy Policy and these Terms of Service.</p>

          <h2>4. Community Standards</h2>
          <p>You agree not to:</p>
          <p>Post content that is unlawful, offensive, defamatory, or infringes on others' rights.</p>
          <p>Use the Services to distribute spam, malware, or harmful content.</p>
          <p>Attempt to access or collect data from other users without permission.</p>
          <p>Violate these Terms or any applicable laws.</p>
          <p>We may remove content or suspend accounts that violate these standards, with or without notice.</p>

          <h2>5. Arbitration and Dispute Resolution</h2>
          <p>Binding Arbitration: Any disputes arising from these Terms or your use of the Services will be resolved through binding arbitration, except for claims that can be filed in small claims court. Arbitration will be conducted in accordance with the rules of the American Arbitration Association in California, USA.</p>
