          <p>We may suspend or terminate your account for violating these Terms, with or without notice. You may delete your account at any time by contacting learnwithlinguid@gmail.com. Upon termination, your license to use the Services ends, but certain provisions (e.g., arbitration, content licenses) survive.</p>

